Dennis Prager Radio Show
Prager 20140527  3 Ultimate Issues Hour: Intervention

Prager H3: Does God intervene in our personal lives? 
            This is a very tough question, even for Dennis.
        
            Callers weigh in with their thoughts. 

     A Best of Prager Hour. Originally broadcast on June 4, 2013.


Prager 20140527  2 Pure Narcissism

Prager H2: The Santa Barbara mass murderer lived in a world
              of pure narcissism

           The Pope visits the West Bank and Israel.
            The reporting of the event reveals a lot about 
               the liberal bias of the international press


Prager 20140527  1 Murder in Santa Barbara

Prager H1: A disturbed narcissist who perceived himself as a victim
            took his anger out on six innocent people.

           Mass murder is becoming a new form of self-expression.
